'''安德烈·李·罗伯森'''（{{lang-en|'''André Lee Roberson'''}}，{{bd|1991年|12月4日||}}），美国职业篮球运动员，目前為自由球員。大学效力并毕业于[[科羅拉多大學|科羅拉多大學]]，以防守為擅。2016年在[[凱文·杜蘭特|凱文·杜蘭特]]離開雷霆後，成為雷霆不可或缺的重要角色。

==高中生涯==
罗伯森高中效力于圣安东尼奥郊区的{{link-en|科伦·瓦格纳高中|Karen Wagner High School}}，在他的四年级赛季，他场均可以拿到15分12个篮板外加1.7次盖帽<ref name=BIO>{{cite web | title = #21 André Roberson | work = CUBuffs.com | url = http://www.cubuffs.com/ViewArticle.dbml?DB_OEM_ID=600&ATCLID=204970260 | accessdate = May 4, 2013 | archive-date = 2016-05-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160531135100/http://www.cubuffs.com/ViewArticle.dbml?DB_OEM_ID=600&ATCLID=204970260 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==大学生涯==
罗伯森选择加入了{{link-en|泰德·博伊尔|Tad Boyle}}教练执教的科罗拉多大学，他成为了球队的头号[[篮板球|篮板球]]手，且在{{link-en|2011-12 NCAA赛季|2011–12 NCAA Division I men's basketball season}}在全国篮板榜排名第三，在{{link-en|2012-13 NCAA赛季|2012–13 NCAA Division I men's basketball season}}的全国篮板榜上位居第二，罗伯森还带领水牛队连续两年杀入NCAA锦标赛<ref name=BIO>{{cite web | title = #21 André Roberson | work = CUBuffs.com | url = http://www.cubuffs.com/ViewArticle.dbml?DB_OEM_ID=600&ATCLID=204970260 | accessdate = May 4, 2013}}</ref>。

在罗伯森的大四赛季，罗伯森场均能贡献10.9分外加11.2个篮板球<ref>{{cite web| title =26号新秀安德烈-罗伯森 小传| work =NBA.com，中文| date =2013-06-28| url =http://china.nba.com/news/4/2013-06-28/draft/26.html| accessdate =2014-09-27| archive-date =2013-09-23| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130923120743/http://china.nba.com/news/4/2013-06-28/draft/26.html| dead-url =no}}</ref>，再次入选太平洋12分区最佳阵容，并且当选了太平洋12分区年度防守球员<ref>{{cite web | last =Eric | first =Carson | title =CU Buffs' Andre Roberson named Pac-12 defensive player of the year | work =DenverPost.com | date =2013-03-21 | url =http://www.denverpost.com/cu/ci_22768520/cu-buffs-andre-roberson-named-pac-12-defensive | accessdate =2014-09-27 | archive-date =2016-03-03 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221954/http://www.denverpost.com/cu/ci_22768520/cu-buffs-andre-roberson-named-pac-12-defensive | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

==职业生涯==

2013年4月28日，羅伯森宣佈放棄他第四年的大學學業，參加2013年NBA選秀[4][5]。在2013年NBA選秀上，羅伯森在第26順位被明尼蘇達森林狼摘下，隨後送至俄克拉何馬城雷霆[6][7]。

2013年7月13日，雷霆隊總經理薩姆·普雷斯蒂宣佈，球隊已經簽下了羅伯森，7月27日，費城問詢報跟進報告稱，羅伯森的合同是標準的80%[注 1]。在羅伯森的新秀賽季，他總計被8次下放到{{link-en|图尔萨66人|Tulsa 66ers}}（雷霆的發展聯盟下屬球隊）<ref>{{cite web| 1 = | title = 雷霆下放安德烈-罗伯森至发展联盟| work = 虎扑体育| date = 2013-12-04| url = http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1568132.html| accessdate = 2014-09-27| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304190559/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1568132.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| 1 = | title = 雷霆第二次下放安德烈-罗伯森至发展联盟| work = 虎扑体育| date = 2014-01-11| url = http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1598533.html| accessdate = 2014-09-27| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195814/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1598533.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| 1 = | title = 雷霆赛季第三次下放安德烈-罗伯森至发展联盟| work = 虎扑体育| date = 2014-01-18| url = http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1606803.html| accessdate = 2014-09-27| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120157/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1606803.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| 1 = | title = 雷霆第4次下放安德烈-罗伯森至NBDL| work = 虎扑体育| date = 2014-01-28| url = http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1614234.html| accessdate = 2014-09-27| archive-date = 2018-11-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181123025814/https://voice.hupu.com/nba/1614234.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| 1 = | title = 雷霆赛季第五次下放安德烈-罗伯森至发展联盟| work = 虎扑体育| date = 2014-02-04| url = http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1618639.html| accessdate = 2014-09-27| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304185026/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1618639.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| 1 = | title = 雷霆第6次下放安德烈-罗伯森至NBDL| work = 虎扑体育| date = 2014-02-08| url = http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1620471.html| accessdate = 2014-09-27| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191444/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1620471.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| 1 = | title = 雷霆第七次下放安德烈-罗伯森至NBDL| work = 虎扑体